{"tid":2284122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［如沐春風］鄧麗欣曬甜笑「獨照」 男友王子醋問：為什麼把我cut掉？？？","createTime":"2020-11-13T05:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T18:13:03.000Z","uid":56716,"like":232,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d58795d611682a9e9a29775b113129fc28939678","tid":2284122,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"鄧麗欣（Stephy）與台灣藝人邱勝翊（王子）發展姊弟戀兩年多，一直愛得甜蜜。因疫情關係二人已九個月沒有見面，靠視像通話來維繫感情。Stephy昨日在其社交平台張貼兩張笑得關懷的獨照，表示感謝一直讓她快樂的人，未料此舉竟惹王子醋意大發，追問「為什麼我在旁邊把我cut掉」。由二人留言互動可見距離並不影響彼此感情，王子一直令Stephy很快樂呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERwaXMh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERwaXMh.png&h=c3771f01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gf3yjD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gf3yjD.png&h=1096e248&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dN7adjE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdN7adjE.png&h=7beed425&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnWFAx0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnWFAx0.png&h=e0da452f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7e3cc8bf8f82f2b213899845f85fc7d969bf637","tid":2284122,"uid":2419,"like":24,"dislike":54,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"死mk食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"44e8fb6dac46b003af8f3147adb0c24977755a06","tid":2284122,"uid":56716,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"c7e3cc8bf8f82f2b213899845f85fc7d969bf637","tid":2284122,"uid":2419,"like":24,"dislike":54,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"死mk食撚屎啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"濛犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話欣定王子？"},{"pid":"8e3c69d1dc9c170e2e3c4a4c299091aae7065daa","tid":2284122,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44e8fb6dac46b003af8f3147adb0c24977755a06","tid":2284122,"uid":56716,"